WEBVTT

00:02:58.792 --> 00:03:00.893
"Sir, you have no shame.

00:03:00.917 --> 00:03:02.678
(In Yoruba: You have no fear of God.)

00:03:02.678 --> 00:03:03.976
You have no fear of God."

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:08.893
Thirty-five thousand Nigerian doctors
are presently working in the US,

00:03:08.917 --> 00:03:10.351
the UK and Canada,

00:03:10.375 --> 00:03:12.018
doing amazing things,

00:03:12.042 --> 00:03:15.184
because in Nigeria,
they are not well-paid,

00:03:15.208 --> 00:03:17.351
neither do they have
the necessary equipment

00:03:17.375 --> 00:03:19.643
to do the job of being a doctor.

00:03:19.667 --> 00:03:23.518
And this is happening
in many African countries.

00:03:23.542 --> 00:03:26.434
We have the capacity to fly.

00:03:26.458 --> 00:03:30.851
But sadly, a lot of African talent
is flying straight out of Africa